Dave Coulier https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dave_Coulier 0 David Alan Coulier (born September 21, 1959) is an American actor, voice actor, stand-up comedian, impressionist and television host. He is well known for playing Joey Gladstone on the ABC sitcom Full House and for voicing Peter Venkman on the cartoon adaptation of Ghostbusters and the infant incarnations of Kermit the Frog, Animal and Bunsen on Muppet Babies.
